1. Dobili smo *pojačanje* u timu. (*We got reinforcement in the team.*)
2. Molim te da mi daš *pojačanje* zvuka. (*Please give me sound amplification.*)
3. Naša firma će zaposliti novo *pojačanje*. (*Our company will hire a new reinforcement.*)
4. Treba mi *pojačanje* za ovaj posao. (*I need assistance for this job.*)
5. Nismo uspeli da pobedimo jer nismo imali dovoljno *pojačanja*. (*We didn't win because we didn't have enough reinforcements.*)
6. *Pojačanje* za zidove kuće je veoma važno. (*Reinforcement for the walls of the house is very important.*)
7. Svi su bili impresionirani kada su videli *pojačanje* koje smo uneli u tim. (*Everyone was impressed when they saw the reinforcement we brought to the team.*)
8. Da bismo dobili ovaj posao, potrebno je da imamo dovoljno *pojačanja*. (*To get this job, we need enough assistance.*)
9. Molim te da mi daš *pojačanje* u vidu saveta. (*Please give me reinforcement in the form of advice.*)
10. Uspeli smo da pobedimo zahvaljujući dobrim *pojačanjima* u timu. (*We managed to win thanks to good reinforcements in the team.*)